reviews.review_text: For completists only-based on sound quality. The composite source is slightly better than this.
APB Wheres Hes Gone for Pig?

He's Gone Was not played for the 1st time after Pig's death until 3/19/73, belatedly perhaps but you must remember the song was initially about Lenny Hart and only later became an anthem for fallen soldiers.....certainly the intense emotion of the 3/24/73 version conveys the heaviness of new meanings revealed.

Check out the SBD portion Everyone if you've never heard this before go check out The Other One on the SBD copy of this show-- it has to be easily one of the best under the radar performances of that song I've ever heard. Five stars for The Other One; seriously, CC would not lie to you!!
